author: etnu
msg: Small patch to improve configurability of core servlets. JsServlet can now have a GagdetFeatureRegistry injected, and GadgetRenderingServlet now takes an entire GadgetServer instance rather than individual components. These changes make writing filters or using custom servlet containers more efficient.
